column5: Hey guys:  Can anyone reccomend a place near Lake Simcoe ( Gilford / Innisfil area ) that I could store my hut. Any help would be greatly appreciated.  Thanks Don
on the 5 line of Innisfil east of highway 11 on the south side of the road there is a farm that always has many different huts stored there I have never seen a sign or name or phone numbe
Thanks Terry - I'll try to find it. Do you remember if its between #11 and 20 sideroad, or between 20 sideroad and the lake.  Don
it's between 11 and the 20  I think there are some cars stored there too
Thanks again Terry - I'll see if I can find it.  Don
